---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About the Firm — RADIANX CAPITAL"
  description="Team, history and values of RADIANX CAPITAL, a New York SEC-registered investment adviser."
  currentPath="/about"
>



<!-- PAGE HEADER -->
<header class="page-header">
  <div class="ph-geo-atm"></div>
  <div class="ph-geo">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 600" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" fill="none">
      <g transform="translate(1180,300)">
        <g class="rot">
          <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="260" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.025)" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M0,-260 A260,260 0 0,1 184,184" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.055)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </g>
        <g class="rotr">
          <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="320" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.015)" stroke-width="1" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="3,8"/>
        </g>
      </g>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="ph-inner">
    <div class="ph-tag rv">About the Firm</div>
    <h1 class="ph-h rv">
      Built on<br><em>conviction.</em>
    </h1>
    <p class="ph-desc rv">
      RADIANX CAPITAL was founded on a simple belief: that high-net-worth individuals deserve the same caliber of investment management and financial counsel previously reserved for the largest institutional investors.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="ph-scroll">
    <div class="ph-scroll-line"></div>
    Scroll
  </div>
</header>

<!-- PHOTO STRIP -->
<div style="position:relative;height:45vh;min-height:320px;overflow:hidden;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(238,240,245,.08)">
  <img src="/images/photo-nyc.jpg" alt="New York City" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;filter:brightness(.45) saturate(.7)">
  <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(7,8,12,.8) 0%,rgba(7,8,12,.2) 60%)"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;left:60px;bottom:48px;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(28px,3.5vw,52px);font-weight:300;color:#fff;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-.5px">
    New York, NY<br><em style="font-style:italic;opacity:.6">Since November 2017.</em>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- INTRO + STATS -->
<section class="intro">
  <div>
    <div class="sec-tag rv">Our Story</div>
    <h2 class="sec-h rv">A firm built for<br><em>the long term</em></h2>
    <p class="body-t rv">
      Founded in New York in November 2017, RADIANX CAPITAL was established to close the gap between institutional investment management and private wealth — bringing genuine analytical rigor, transparent pricing, and unwavering fiduciary commitment to discerning clients.
    </p>
    <p class="body-t rv">
      Over eight years, we have grown to manage nearly $1 billion in assets while maintaining the operational discipline, selectivity, and personal attention that define who we are. Our clients are not account numbers — they are long-term partners.
    </p>
    <p class="body-t rv">
      We are registered with the SEC (No. 801-117100), held to the highest regulatory standards, and bound by an absolute fiduciary duty to every client we serve.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="intro-stats rv">
    <div class="i-stat">
      <div class="i-stat-n">$953<sup>M+</sup></div>
      <div class="i-stat-info">
        <div class="i-stat-l">Assets Under Management</div>
        <div class="i-stat-d">As of most recent SEC Form ADV filing</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="i-stat">
      <div class="i-stat-n">8<sup>+</sup></div>
      <div class="i-stat-info">
        <div class="i-stat-l">Years in Operation</div>
        <div class="i-stat-d">Established November 13, 2017</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="i-stat">
      <div class="i-stat-n">100<sup>%</sup></div>
      <div class="i-stat-info">
        <div class="i-stat-l">Fiduciary Standard</div>
        <div class="i-stat-d">No commissions. No conflicts. Always.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="i-stat">
      <div class="i-stat-n">SEC</div>
      <div class="i-stat-info">
        <div class="i-stat-l">Registered Investment Adviser</div>
        <div class="i-stat-d">CRD# 298178 · SEC# 801-117100</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- VALUES -->
<section class="values">
  <div class="values-head">
    <div>
      <div class="sec-tag rv">What We Stand For</div>
      <h2 class="sec-h rv" style="margin-bottom:0">Our core<br><em>principles</em></h2>
    </div>
    <p class="body-t rv" style="padding-top:56px">
      These principles are not aspirational statements posted on a wall. They are the operational standards by which every client relationship, every investment decision, and every internal process is conducted.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="values-grid">
    <div class="val rv">
      <div class="val-top"></div>
      <div class="val-num">01</div>
      <div class="val-t">Fiduciary Obligation</div>
      <div class="val-d">We are legally and morally bound to act solely in your best interest. There are no proprietary products to push, no referral fees to chase — just expert counsel aligned entirely with your outcomes.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="val rv d1">
      <div class="val-top"></div>
      <div class="val-num">02</div>
      <div class="val-t">Disciplined Precision</div>
      <div class="val-d">Every portfolio, every plan, every recommendation is constructed with methodological rigor. We measure what matters, we stress-test our assumptions, and we never confuse activity with progress.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="val rv d2">
      <div class="val-top"></div>
      <div class="val-num">03</div>
      <div class="val-t">Long-Term Thinking</div>
      <div class="val-d">Wealth is not built in a quarter. We make decisions based on your long-term financial architecture — not short-term market noise, not performance chasing, not calendar-driven activity.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="val rv">
      <div class="val-top"></div>
      <div class="val-num">04</div>
      <div class="val-t">Radical Transparency</div>
      <div class="val-d">Our fee structures are straightforward and disclosed upfront. Our communications are direct. You will always know the reasoning behind every recommendation we make.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="val rv d1">
      <div class="val-top"></div>
      <div class="val-num">05</div>
      <div class="val-t">Selectivity</div>
      <div class="val-d">We maintain a deliberately limited client roster. This allows us to deliver the depth of attention each relationship deserves — and to hold every client to the same high standard of partnership.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="val rv d2">
      <div class="val-top"></div>
      <div class="val-num">06</div>
      <div class="val-t">Regulatory Integrity</div>
      <div class="val-d">SEC registration is not a formality — it is a commitment. We embrace the full scope of our regulatory obligations as a baseline, not a ceiling, for how we conduct business.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TEAM -->
<section class="team" id="team">
  <div class="team-head">
    <div class="sec-tag rv">Leadership</div>
    <h2 class="sec-h rv">The people<br>behind your <em>capital</em></h2>
  </div>
  <div class="team-grid">

    <!-- Li Tan -->
    <div class="member rv">
      <div class="member-top"></div>
      <div class="member-avatar">
        <div class="member-avatar-ring">
          <span class="member-initials">LT</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="member-role">Principal</div>
      <div class="member-name">Li Tan</div>
      <div class="member-title">Co-Founder &amp; Managing Principal</div>
      <p class="member-bio">
        Li Tan brings decades of experience in institutional investment management and private wealth advisory to RADIANX CAPITAL. With a career spanning both domestic and international markets, Li has built a reputation for constructing resilient, tax-efficient portfolios that align closely with each client's long-term financial objectives. His approach combines deep fundamental analysis with disciplined risk management — a methodology refined over more than thirty years in practice.
      </p>
      <div class="member-divider"></div>
      <div class="member-detail">
        <div class="md-row">New York, NY · Over 30 Years of Experience</div>
        <div class="md-row">CRD# 298178 · RADIANX CAPITAL, LLC</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- David Su -->
    <div class="member rv d1">
      <div class="member-top"></div>
      <div class="member-avatar">
        <div class="member-avatar-ring">
          <span class="member-initials">DS</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="member-role">Principal</div>
      <div class="member-name">David Su</div>
      <div class="member-title">Co-Founder &amp; Senior Adviser</div>
      <p class="member-bio">
        David Su is a seasoned wealth management professional whose career has been defined by a rigorous, client-first approach to financial planning and investment oversight. With over three decades of experience serving high-net-worth families and business owners, David specializes in retirement income architecture, estate planning coordination, and the complex financial transitions that accompany major life events. His counsel is grounded in patience, thoroughness, and an unwavering commitment to each client's independence and security.
      </p>
      <div class="member-divider"></div>
      <div class="member-detail">
        <div class="md-row">New York, NY · Over 30 Years of Experience</div>
        <div class="md-row">CRD# 298178 · RADIANX CAPITAL, LLC</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Douglas Beyer -->
    <div class="member rv d2">
      <div class="member-top"></div>
      <div class="member-avatar">
        <div class="member-avatar-ring">
          <span class="member-initials">DB</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="member-role">Adviser</div>
      <div class="member-name">Douglas Beyer</div>
      <div class="member-title">Investment Adviser &amp; Analyst</div>
      <p class="member-bio">
        Douglas Beyer represents the next generation of investment advisory at RADIANX CAPITAL. Combining a strong analytical foundation with a contemporary perspective on portfolio construction and technology-enabled research, Douglas focuses on identifying high-conviction investment opportunities, monitoring market developments, and delivering clear, evidence-based recommendations. He works closely with both principals to ensure every client portfolio remains optimally positioned against evolving market conditions.
      </p>
      <div class="member-divider"></div>
      <div class="member-detail">
        <div class="md-row">New York, NY · Investment Analysis &amp; Advisory</div>
        <div class="md-row">CRD# 298178 · RADIANX CAPITAL, LLC</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TIMELINE -->
<section class="timeline">
  <div class="tl-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="sec-tag rv">Firm History</div>
      <h2 class="sec-h rv">Eight years<br>of <em>measured growth</em></h2>
      <p class="body-t rv" style="margin-top:24px">
        From founding to nearly $1 billion under management — a progression built on trust, not marketing. Each milestone reflects a deepening of client relationships, not a departure from them.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-list rv">
      <div class="tl-item">
        <div class="tl-year">November 2017</div>
        <div class="tl-t">Founded in New York</div>
        <div class="tl-d">RADIANX CAPITAL, LLC is established in New York City by Li Tan and David Su, with a founding mandate to deliver institutional-grade investment management to private clients.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tl-item">
        <div class="tl-year">2018</div>
        <div class="tl-t">SEC Registration</div>
        <div class="tl-d">The firm achieves full registration as a Registered Investment Adviser with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission under No. 801-117100, establishing its fiduciary framework.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tl-item">
        <div class="tl-year">2019 — 2021</div>
        <div class="tl-t">Selective Client Growth</div>
        <div class="tl-d">Assets under management grow steadily as the firm builds a concentrated roster of high-net-worth clients through direct referral. Growth is deliberate — quality of relationship over quantity of accounts.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tl-item">
        <div class="tl-year">2022</div>
        <div class="tl-t">Team Expansion</div>
        <div class="tl-d">Douglas Beyer joins the firm as Investment Adviser and Analyst, strengthening the firm's analytical capacity and enabling deeper research-driven portfolio management for existing clients.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tl-item">
        <div class="tl-year">2024 — 2025</div>
        <div class="tl-t">Approaching $1 Billion AUM</div>
        <div class="tl-d">RADIANX CAPITAL reaches approximately $953 million in assets under management — a milestone that validates the firm's disciplined approach to long-term wealth stewardship.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- COMPLIANCE -->
<section class="compliance">
  <div>
    <div class="sec-tag rv">Regulatory Standing</div>
    <h2 class="sec-h rv">Full disclosure.<br><em>No exceptions.</em></h2>
    <p class="body-t rv">
      Our regulatory status is available in full through the SEC's Investment Adviser Public Disclosure system. We encourage prospective clients to review our Form ADV, which details our business practices, fee structures, and any relevant disciplinary history.
    </p>
    <p class="body-t rv">
      Transparency is not a marketing position at RADIANX CAPITAL — it is a regulatory obligation we embrace completely.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="compliance-grid rv">
    <div class="cg">
      <div class="cg-l">Legal Entity</div>
      <div class="cg-v">RADIANX CAPITAL, LLC</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cg">
      <div class="cg-l">Entity Type</div>
      <div class="cg-v">Limited Liability Company</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cg">
      <div class="cg-l">SEC Number</div>
      <div class="cg-v">801-117100</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cg">
      <div class="cg-l">CRD Number</div>
      <div class="cg-v">298178</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cg">
      <div class="cg-l">EIN</div>
      <div class="cg-v">82-3414149</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cg">
      <div class="cg-l">Established</div>
      <div class="cg-v">November 13, 2017</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cg">
      <div class="cg-l">Registered Address</div>
      <div class="cg-v">529 5th Ave, Suite 1475<br>New York, NY 10017</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cg">
      <div class="cg-l">Direct Line</div>
      <div class="cg-v">(646) 403-3807</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="cta">
  <div class="cta-geo">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 360 360" fill="none">
      <circle cx="180" cy="180" r="150" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
      <path d="M180,30 A150,150 0 0,1 330,180" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      <circle cx="180" cy="30" r="5" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <h2 class="cta-h rv">
    Ready to discuss<br>your <em>financial future?</em>
  </h2>
  <div class="cta-right rv">
    <p class="cta-body">
      We offer a complimentary initial consultation to qualified prospective clients. No obligation, no pressure — just an honest conversation about where you are and where you want to be.
    </p>
    <div class="cta-btns">
      <a href="tel:6464033807" class="btn-a">Call (646) 403-3807</a>
      <a href="mailto:invest@radianx.io" class="btn-b">Email Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->

</div>

</Layout>

<style is:global>

/* ═══ PAGE HEADER ═══ */
.page-header{
  padding:200px 60px 100px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--brd);
}
.ph-geo{position:absolute;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:0}
.ph-geo svg{width:100%;height:100%}
.ph-geo-atm{
  position:absolute;top:-10%;right:-8%;width:50%;height:70%;
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 65% 25%,rgba(122,150,168,.04) 0%,transparent 65%);
  pointer-events:none;z-index:0;
}
.ph-inner{position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:860px}
.ph-tag{
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--white3);margin-bottom:28px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;
}
.ph-tag::before{content:'';width:28px;height:1px;background:var(--accent);opacity:.6}
.ph-h{
  font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(54px,6.5vw,96px);
  font-weight:300;line-height:.95;letter-spacing:-2px;margin-bottom:44px;
}
.ph-h em{font-style:italic;color:var(--white2)}
.ph-desc{
  font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:300;
  color:var(--white2);line-height:1.8;max-width:600px;
}

/* scroll indicator inline */
.ph-scroll{
  position:absolute;bottom:36px;right:60px;z-index:1;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--white3);text-transform:uppercase;
}
.ph-scroll-line{width:30px;height:1px;background:var(--white3);animation:sp 2.5s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes sp{0%,100%{transform:scaleX(1);opacity:.3}50%{transform:scaleX(1.5);opacity:.6}}

/* ═══ INTRO / TWO-COL ═══ */
.intro{
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:100px;padding:110px 60px;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--brd);
  align-items:start;
}
.sec-tag{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--white3);margin-bottom:26px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
.sec-tag::before{content:'';width:28px;height:1px;background:var(--accent);opacity:.6}
.sec-h{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(34px,3.5vw,52px);font-weight:300;line-height:1.12;margin-bottom:28px;letter-spacing:-.3px}
.sec-h em{font-style:italic;color:var(--white2)}
.body-t{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:300;color:var(--white2);line-height:1.82;margin-bottom:18px}

/* vertical divider stat */
.intro-stats{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0}
.i-stat{
  padding:36px 0;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--brd2);
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr;
  gap:28px;align-items:center;
  transition:padding-left .25s;cursor:none;
}
.i-stat:first-child{border-top:1px solid var(--brd2)}
.i-stat:hover{padding-left:12px}
.i-stat-n{
  font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(40px,3.5vw,56px);
  font-weight:300;color:var(--white);line-height:1;
  min-width:110px;
}
.i-stat-n sup{font-size:.4em;color:var(--white3);vertical-align:top;margin-top:.15em}
.i-stat-info{}
.i-stat-l{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--white3);margin-bottom:4px}
.i-stat-d{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:13px;font-weight:300;color:rgba(240,238,235,.38);line-height:1.6}

/* ═══ VALUES ═══ */
.values{
  padding:110px 60px;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--brd);
  background:var(--bg2);
}
.values-head{
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 2fr;
  gap:80px;align-items:start;margin-bottom:72px;
}
.values-grid{
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
  gap:1px;background:var(--brd);border:1px solid var(--brd);
}
.val{
  background:var(--bg2);padding:48px 36px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  transition:background .3s;cursor:none;
}
.val:hover{background:var(--bg3)}
.val-top{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:var(--accent);transform:scaleX(0);transform-origin:left;transition:transform .45s;opacity:.5}
.val:hover .val-top{transform:scaleX(1)}
.val-num{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--white3);margin-bottom:30px;opacity:.6}
.val-t{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:22px;font-weight:400;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:14px;line-height:1.2}
.val-d{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:13.5px;font-weight:300;color:var(--white3);line-height:1.7}

/* ═══ TEAM ═══ */
.team{padding:110px 60px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--brd)}
.team-head{margin-bottom:68px}
.team-grid{
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
  gap:1px;background:var(--brd);border:1px solid var(--brd);
}
.member{
  background:var(--bg);padding:52px 40px 44px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  transition:background .3s;cursor:none;
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;
}
.member:hover{background:var(--bg2)}
.member-top{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:var(--accent);transform:scaleX(0);transform-origin:left;transition:transform .5s;opacity:.5}
.member:hover .member-top{transform:scaleX(1)}

/* Avatar — geometric initials, not a photo */
.member-avatar{
  width:64px;height:64px;margin-bottom:32px;
  position:relative;flex-shrink:0;
}
.member-avatar-ring{
  width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:50%;
  border:1px solid var(--brd);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  transition:border-color .3s;
}
.member:hover .member-avatar-ring{border-color:var(--accent-brd)}
.member-initials{
  font-family:var(--serif);font-size:22px;font-weight:300;
  color:var(--white2);letter-spacing:.5px;
}

.member-role{
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2.5px;
  text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--white3);margin-bottom:10px;
}
.member-name{
  font-family:var(--serif);font-size:30px;font-weight:400;
  color:var(--white);margin-bottom:6px;line-height:1.1;
}
.member-title{
  font-family:var(--sans);font-size:13.5px;font-weight:400;
  color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:24px;letter-spacing:.2px;
}
.member-bio{
  font-family:var(--sans);font-size:13.5px;font-weight:300;
  color:var(--white3);line-height:1.72;flex:1;
}
.member-divider{width:24px;height:1px;background:var(--brd);margin:26px 0}
.member-detail{
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;
}
.md-row{
  display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:1.2px;color:rgba(240,238,235,.3);
}
.md-row::before{content:'—';color:rgba(240,238,235,.15);flex-shrink:0}

/* ═══ TIMELINE ═══ */
.timeline{
  padding:110px 60px;
  background:var(--bg2);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--brd);
}
.tl-inner{
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 2fr;
  gap:100px;align-items:start;
}
.tl-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;position:relative}
.tl-list::before{
  content:'';position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;
  width:1px;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,var(--brd2),var(--brd),var(--brd2));
}
.tl-item{
  padding:32px 0 32px 36px;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--brd2);
  position:relative;
  transition:padding-left .25s;cursor:none;
}
.tl-item:hover{padding-left:44px}
.tl-item::before{
  content:'';position:absolute;
  left:-3px;top:40px;
